<br />
<br />I also notice a huge difference going between composite and S-Video.  S-Video does not have the "walking ants" effect on solid lines the way composite has.  Maybe the best thing out there is an RGB mod -&gt; Svideo conversion.    <img src="./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif" alt=":lol:" title="Laughing" />

		

